Package org.apache.log4j

Class Level

java.lang.Object
org.apache.log4j.Level
Direct Known Subclasses:
Priority
public class Level extends Object
Log4j Level compatibility class that maps to log4Rich LogLevel. Provides drop-in replacement for org.apache.log4j.Level.
